				<div class="rt-headline"><h1 class="rt-article-title">Property Management Services</h1>		</div>
		<div class="clear"></div>
				<div class="rt-article-content">
					
										
			<p><img src="images/stories/demo/frontpage/property_management_large.jpg" border="0" style="float: right; border-width: 0px;" /><br /><strong>Universe Consultant, Inc.,</strong> led by founder and CEO, Marilyn Llanes, along with her years of experience in the Property Management industry, is ready and eager to cater to your community association management needs.  Our Company is structured so that our “boutique” approach of work gives our communities the exclusiveness and the customized service they may need without paying high boutique costs. Every community, big or small, is treated as if they were our only customer with their interests placed ahead of anything else.<br /><br />Our staff works diligently, effectively and thoroughly and is focused on delivering innovative solutions to all of your communities needs.  It is our objective to provide unparallel customer service in the most cost-effective manner while balancing the importance of quality.  <br /><br />Our dedication to the details that impact the value of your assets depicts our commitment to protecting your community.  Our number one goal is to provide our customers with more than they would ever expect and deliver in a timely manner with consistency, precision, incomparable loyalty.</p>
			
					</div>
		
