<div class="rt-article ">
	<div class="rt-article-bg">
	
				<div class="rt-headline"><h1 class="rt-article-title">As your Property Management Firm we will:</h1>		</div>
		<div class="clear"></div>
				<div class="rt-article-content">
					
										
			<p><img src="images/stories/demo/frontpage/Property Management.jpg" border="0" style="float: right; border-width: 0px;" /></p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-1.png" border="0" /> Assist the Board of Directors in a competitive bidding process for non-emergency services, and provide input in selection of contractors and vendors.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-2.png" border="0" /> Obtain from each contractor relevant certificates of insurance and licenses.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-3.png" border="0" /> Perform regular site inspections in order to maintain a satisfactory knowledge of the condition of the property and performance of the contractors.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-4.png" border="0" /> Receive service requests for repairs or maintenance of property and report trends in service requests to the Board of Directors.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-5.png" border="0" /> Advise the Board of Directors of major problems or trends in maintenance service requests as they occur.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-6.png" border="0" /> Arrange for prompt and satisfactory response to emergency service requests.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-7.png" border="0" /> Provide and monitor our 24 hour emergency telephone service.</p>
			
					</div>
		
				<div class="clear"></div>
	</div>
</div>									
<div class="rt-article ">
	<div class="rt-article-bg">
	
				<div class="rt-headline"><h1 class="rt-article-title">We provide your community with Financial Management Service such as:</h1>		</div>
		<div class="clear"></div>
				<div class="rt-article-content">
					
										
			<p><br /><img src="images/stories/Financial Management .jpg" border="0" style="float: right; border-width: 0px;" /></p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-1.png" border="0" /> Assist in the development and preparation of the annual operating budget.<br /><br /><img src="images/stories/number-2.png" border="0" /> Prepare a mailing to owners of the approved budget if requested by the Board of Directors.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-3.png" border="0" /> Prepare and submit a Year-To-Date Budgeted versus Actual Income and Expense analysis on a monthly basis as a part of the monthly financial statements.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-4.png" border="0" /> Prepare and maintain books and records necessary to produce Financial Statements.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-5.png" border="0" /> Prepare and submit a monthly financial summary of all receipts and disbursements.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-6.png" border="0" /> Receive, review and approve vendor invoices and other bills, and prepare checks for payment and subsequent mailing.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-7.png" border="0" /> Collect all assessments as they become due and payable.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-8.png" border="0" /> Maintain a record of homeowner’s dues and receipts, and provide a monthly delinquency listing. We can set up a monthly mailing for the late notices.</p>
<p> </p>
			
					</div>
		
				<div class="clear"></div>
	</div>
