			<p><img src="images/stories/legal representation1.jpg" border="0" style="float: right;" />Assist as necessary to initiate required legal action consistent with the Association's By-Laws, Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions.<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /></p>
			
