<p><img src="images/stories/number-2.png" border="0" /> Assist and advise in the preparation of general correspondence between residents, owners, contractors, etc. We will keep a record of all correspondence received or issued.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-3.png" border="0" /> Assist in the procurement of insurance coverage, as well as the processing of insurance claims.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-4.png" border="0" /> Attend and assist in coordinating general membership meetings, including the Annual Meeting.<br /><br /><img src="images/stories/number-5.png" border="0" /> Perform background checks on all buyers and/or renters.</p>
<p><img src="images/stories/number-6.png" border="0" /> Carry out all duties required by the association prior to closing on a unit; estoppel letters, condo questionnaires, application fees, background check, etc…</p>
